<br />\n做枱枱櫈櫈職位既<br />\n<br />\n一律3.5%<br />\n<br />\n問題就來喇<br />\n<br />\n加完條ive仔人工<br />\n<br />\n佢竟然出聲問我可唔可以加多d比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca8094f9697601e544672ee86b87183ce63024e","tid":208940,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T00:24:15.000Z","msg":"公司全年開資預好晒<br />\n<br />\n無得多<br />\n<br />\n要我加人工比件ive仔<br />\n<br />\n即係要我減其他人人工再加比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就搵佢入房傾啦<br />\n<br />\n問佢點解要再加多d人工比佢<br />\n<br />\n佢話自己幫公司賺好多錢<br />\n<br />\n佢話有幾份award左既tender都係佢報既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果度佢幫公司賺左80萬喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58aadeace7f1fc0634ba811700c93bd548f245eb","tid":208940,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T00:27:48.000Z","msg":"一聽到真係谷鳩氣<br />\n<br />\n平時細既報價係佢預備之後我簽名再出街<br />\n<br />\n但係Tender唔可以出錯<br />\n<br />\n我全部自己準備<br />\n<br />\n條ive仔既角色只係速遞<br />\n<br />\n佢就講到tender係佢報既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要幫公司賺左錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0ba2a8ea2761a36c2e5ca5a49337d1662e7b55","tid":208940,"uid":70192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T00:28:49.000Z","msg":"找數未"},{"pid":"d7258109c56a18cbe92128b51459895bf377f87c","tid":208940,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T00:29:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>找數未</blockquote><br />\n開左盤鬥捐錢<br />\n<br />\n有條柒頭唔敢受又唔認輸"},{"pid":"0d5e99d58643a9b8090a894cda29c93f50af381c","tid":208940,"uid":24759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T00:31:58.000Z","msg":"留名睇戲"},{"pid":"cc386875808b277674f540f3bad4d05b634f7694","tid":208940,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T00:32:20.000Z","msg":"你買張枱返來<br /