3","tid":208940,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:29:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>米蛇等緊你呀屈星如</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都係想睇人鬥捐錢姐<br />\n<br />\n比我挑緊條柒頭回應左先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢一世唔回應你係咪一世唔使面對米sir？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比個限期好</blockquote><br />\n無期限<br />\n<br />\n有條柒頭當我開始同米已成炊傾佢就突個龜頭出來抽水<br />\n<br />\n你地無花生食<br />\n<br />\n去怪兩條柒頭</blockquote><br />\n你條弱智走數狗，挑我唔係問題呀。<br />\n人地米蛇開擂台在先，屌你老母搵我做擋箭牌避米蛇？<br />\n我包你去到連登都做過街老鼠，無人不識。你每個post我都貼你d精華柒事出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd302872f0f0c46ddd82087aeeb8affc96babb78","tid":208940,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇簡介<br />\n係咪上次吹到好勁一開波就捐錢點知比人反cup個2個</blockquote><br />\n劇情回顧:<br />\n屈機男在高登常以有錢佬姿態教化高登仔做人道理<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R0i1Q28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR0i1Q28.jpg&h=c884d968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屈機男常自稱有幾個物業, 但又睇淡樓市<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W1Bp683.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW1Bp683.jpg&h=14ab5e98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/69n6byc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F69n6byc.jpg&h=508c64cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屈機男以高高在上姿態雄霸財經台, 而且有一眾信眾追隨.<br />\n然而, 直至會員 米已成炊出現, 他質疑屈機男之有錢言論, 多次挑戰其財經台權威.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3u76373.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3u76373.jpg&h=476a844a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是大發明家屈機男發明了解決糾紛方法...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ly869i3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLy869i3.jpg&h=be0daf5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/009PHw5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F009PHw5.jpg&h=dcad78a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屈機男及其信眾一直強勢, 欺侮米已成炊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKrCVnV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKrCVnV.jpg&h=33bd4d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgX65WO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgX65WO.jpg&h=c0ddb46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVg6J3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVg6J3M.jpg&h=f50358a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都係直接飛到結局.... 屈機男捐唔起錢認輸, 而其信眾亦鳥獸散或深潛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6d859G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6d859G.jpg&h=bb060f2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pw1pgUy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPw1pgUy.jpg&h=7c7dbc8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q8NL1v6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq8NL1v6.png&h=401336d2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fde7d162b06f677e1373324066f1ef2f8495c509","tid":208940,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:30:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>走數狗屈機男 信佢果個真係要驗腦</blockquote><br />\n弱智<br />\n<br />\n岩岩先ko左件阿域<br />\n<br />\n另外，我走左邊條數？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/009PHw5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F009PHw5.jpg&h=dcad78a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明話輸左永久退出高登, 但又定期上水留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Opwr82D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOpwr82D.jpg&h=d8cfee